'''Orangina'''（{{IPA-fr|ɔʁɑ̃ʒina}}）是一種[[碳酸飲料|碳酸飲料]]，原料包括碳酸水、12%的柑橘果汁（10%是濃縮[[橙汁|橙汁]]，2%是濃縮[[檸檬|檸檬]]汁、[[橘|橘]]汁、[[葡萄柚汁|葡萄柚汁]]的混合果汁）、2%的橙子果肉<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://orangina.eu/products/original |title=Orangina |publisher=Orangina.eu |access-date=2017-07-24 |archive-date=2020-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812024635/http://orangina.eu/products/original |dead-url=no }}</ref>。Orangina使用糖或[[高果糖漿|高果糖漿]]增甜，並添加天然香料<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cdmproductfacts.ca/en/product/ORANGINA_296|title=Canada Dry Mott's Product Facts|website=www.cdmproductfacts.ca|language=en|access-date=2017-07-25|archive-date=2020-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200713170244/https://www.cdmproductfacts.ca/en/product/ORANGINA_296|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Orangina由Augustin Trigo Mirallès在1933年發明於法屬阿爾及利亞。現在Orangina在歐洲（特別是法國和瑞士）、日本、北非、北美等地銷售。

2009年11月開始，Orangina在世界上大部分地區由[[三得利|三得利]]所有<ref name="Suntory snaps" />。在美國和加拿大，該品牌由三得利所有，並自2020年開始授權Ventures Food and Beverage生產<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|date=2020-03-05|title=Ventures Food and Beverage Acquires Licensing to Orangina for North American Reintroduction|url=https://www.bevnet.com/news/2020/ventures-food-and-beverage-acquires-licensing-to-orangina-for-north-american-reintroduction|access-date=2022-01-08|website=BevNET.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220226234015/https://www.bevnet.com/news/2020/ventures-food-and-beverage-acquires-licensing-to-orangina-for-north-american-reintroduction|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此前該品牌曾由{{link-en|Dr Pepper Snapple集團|Dr Pepper Snapple Group}}和{{link-en|Canada Dry Motts|Canada Dry Motts}}生產。

== 歷史 ==
Orangina由來自[[瓦倫西亞|瓦倫西亞]]的西班牙人化學家奧古斯汀·特里戈（Augustin Trigo）發明<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.orangina.eu/en/our-history/|title=The History of Orangina|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121202182823/http://www.orangina.eu/en/our-history/|archive-date=2012-12-02}}</ref>。其第一次問世是在1936年[[馬賽|馬賽]]貿易展上。這座飲料由柑橘汁、[[醣|醣]]和[[碳酸水|碳酸水]]製作<ref name="nytimes" />。其後該飲料以TriNaranjus（現TriNa）的名稱在西班牙市場上銷售。

1935年，法國商人萊昂·貝頓（Léon Beton）購買了這一品牌和配方<ref name=nytimes>{{cite news |first=William |last=Yardley |title=Jean-Claude Beton, Who Sent Orangina Around the World, Dies at 88 |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2013/12/07/business/jean-claude-beton-who-gave-orangina-its-signature-bottle-dies-at-88.html?_r=0 |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=2013-12-06 |access-date=2014-01-05 |archive-date=2020-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200716140952/https://www.nytimes.com/2013/12/07/business/jean-claude-beton-who-gave-orangina-its-signature-bottle-dies-at-88.html?_r=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但由於戰爭（特別是[[第二次世界大戰|第二次世界大戰]]）的影響，貝頓在歐洲市場上推廣這一飲料的嘗試受到很大阻礙<ref name=france24/>。

貝頓的兒子{{link-en|尚盧-克勞德·貝頓|Jean-Claude Beton}}在1947年繼承了公司<ref name=nytimes/><ref name=france24>{{cite news |title=Founder of iconic French soda Orangina dies |url=http://www.france24.com/en/20131204-orangina-soft-drink-founder-dies-beton-marseille-france-coke/ |work=[[France_24|France 24]] |date=2013-12-04 |access-date=2014-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180726072026/http://www.france24.com/en/20131204-orangina-soft-drink-founder-dies-beton-marseille-france-coke |archive-date=2018-07-26 |url-status=dead}}</ref>。他保留了原始配方的大部分內容，並在歐洲和北非擴大市場<ref name=nytimes/>。Orangina很快成為[[北非|北非]]的常見飲料<ref name=france24/>。1951年，尚盧-克勞德·貝頓推出了Orangina標誌性的8盎司瓶子，現已成為該品牌象徵<ref name=nytimes/>。瓶子令人想到[[橙子|橙子]]的圓形形狀，玻璃瓶身亦模仿水果<ref name=nytimes/>。

在阿爾及利亞獨立前夕的1962年，Orangina將產地遷至[[法國本土|法國本土]]的[[馬賽|馬賽]]<ref name=nytimes/>。1978年，Orangina在美國上市，最初品牌名為Orelia，後改為Orangina<ref name=nytimes/>。1984年，Orangina加入[[保樂力加|保樂力加]]集團。

2000年，Orangina和保樂力加的其它[[軟飲料|軟飲料]]品牌一併被[[吉百利|吉百利]]收購。此前[[可口可樂公司|可口可樂公司]]曾試圖收購，但因涉嫌壟斷而未能實現<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.nytimes.com/2000/01/26/business/media-business-advertising-orangina-s-owner-still-wants-sell-brand-if-price.html?pagewanted=1 | work=The New York Times | title=Orangina's owner still wants to sell brand, if the price is right | first=Constance L. | last=Hays | date=2000-01-26 | access-date=2010-05-20 | archive-date=2020-11-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107120752/https://www.nytimes.com/2000/01/26/business/media-business-advertising-orangina-s-owner-still-wants-sell-brand-if-price.html?pagewanted=1 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2006年，吉百利決定專注[[巧克力|巧克力]]業務，並出售其飲料部門。

===北美===
在美國，該品牌曾由{{link-en|Dr Pepper Snapple集團|Dr Pepper Snapple Group}}所有<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.drpeppersnapplegroup.com/brands/orangina/|title=Orangina|access-date=2022-03-11|archive-date=2018-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180206131423/https://www.drpeppersnapplegroup.com/brands/orangina|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Orangina最初在加拿大生產<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ft.com/cms/s/2/1e5450d2-2be5-11df-8033-00144feabdc0.html|title=The inside story of the Cadbury takeover|access-date=2022-03-11|archive-date=2016-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160911074235/http://www.ft.com/cms/s/2/1e5450d2-2be5-11df-8033-00144feabdc0.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年開始，三得利取得Orangina在北美的所有權，並授權Ventures Foods and Beverage生產<ref name=":0" />。

===世界其它地區===
2006年開始，[[黑石集團|黑石集團]]和{{link-en|獅子資本|Lion Capital LLP}}收購了Orangina在北美以外的所有權<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.officialwire.com/main.php?action%3Dposted_news%26rid%3D116965%26catid%3D1254|title=Russia Per Distribuire Due Brigate Dell'Esercito in Artico|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927143846/http://www.officialwire.com/main.php?action=posted_news&rid=116965&catid=1254|archive-date=2011-09-27|url-status=dead|access-date=2010-03-30}}</ref>。2009年11月，日本企業[[三得利|三得利]]收購了Orangina品牌<ref name="Suntory snaps">{{cite news | title=Japan's Suntory snaps up Orangina | date=2009-11-13 | publisher=BBC | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/business/8358674.stm | work=BBC News | access-date=2009-11-15 | archive-date=2020-07-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200713203044/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/business/8358674.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在英國，Orangina曾由[[格拉斯哥|格拉斯哥]]的{{link-en|A.G. Barr|A.G. Barr}}公司（[[Irn-Bru|Irn-Bru]]的生產商）生產<ref>{{Cite web|url =http://www.agbarr.co.uk/pdf/Interim%20Report%20for%20the%206%20months%20to%2027%20July%202014.pdf|title =A.G. BARR p.l.c. Interim Report July 2014|access-date =20 January 2015|page =3|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150120170354/http://www.agbarr.co.uk/pdf/Interim%20Report%20for%20the%206%20months%20to%2027%20July%202014.pdf|archive-date =2015-01-02|url-status =dead}}</ref>。

== 廣告 ==
Orangina瓶子底部的果粒曾是其不利特徵。Orangina將其反而作為產品高品質特徵進行宣傳，以「搖我」（Shake me）作為廣告語<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.lexpress.fr/styles/saveurs/la-saga-des-pubs-orangina_1304841.html|title=La saga des publicités Orangina|last=Majoube|first=Ulla|date=2013-12-03|work=L'Express|access-date=2013-12-03|archive-date=2021-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416131541/https://www.lexpress.fr/styles/saveurs/la-saga-des-pubs-orangina_1304841.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年，Orangina發布了一個同性戀友好的廣告<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.digitaljournal.com/article/293882|title=Soft drink ad 'too gay' for French TV|last=Summerton|first=Johnny|date=2010-06-26|work=Digital Journal|access-date=2018-05-15|archive-date=2020-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200713203044/http://www.digitaljournal.com/article/293882|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 批評 ===
2008年，Orangina的一則使用動物形象的廣告因其性暗示內容遭到批評<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/media/advertising/sexual-orangina-ad-angers-viewers-and-childrens-charity-907205.html |title='Sexual' Orangina ad angers viewers and children's charity |work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]] |location=London |date=2008-08-24 |accessdate=2022-03-11 |archive-date=2017-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170701094135/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/media/advertising/sexual-orangina-ad-angers-viewers-and-childrens-charity-907205.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該廣告獲得了「2008年最怪異廣告獎」，並且在「2008年最差電視廣告」排名第七<ref>{{cite news |url=http://adweek.blogs.com/adfreak/freakiest2007/index.html |title=FREAKY AD MOMENTS OF 2007, SWEET 16 |work=[[Adweek|Adweek]] |access-date=2009-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090720223732/http://adweek.blogs.com/adfreak/freakiest2007/index.html |archive-date=2009-07-20 |url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/organgrinder/2008/dec/11/advertising-television |title=Organ Grinder: The worst TV ads of 2008 |work=The Guardian |location=London |first=Mark |last=Sweney |date=2008-12-11 |access-date=2010-05-20 |archive-date=2021-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210305110422/https://www.theguardian.com/media/organgrinder/2008/dec/11/advertising-television |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

但亦有觀點認為Orangina並非是僅面向兒童的飲料，亦是「領先的成人軟飲料」<ref name="talkingretail">{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2008-08-04|title=Orangina launch new advert packed with animal magnetism|url=https://www.talkingretail.com/products-news/orangina-launch-new-advert-packed-with-animal-magnetism-04-08-2008/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201103820/https://www.talkingretail.com/products-news/orangina-launch-new-advert-packed-with-animal-magnetism-04-08-2008/|archive-date=2021-02-01|access-date=2021-02-01|website=Talking Retail}}</ref>。該廣告引發的爭議亦起到了免費宣傳的作用<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thoughtgadgets.com/2008/08/oranginas-beastly-ad-shakes-up-uk.html|title=Orangina's beastly ad shakes up UK|work=Thought Gadgets|date=2008-08-28|author=Ben Kunz|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110717052019/http://www.thoughtgadgets.com/2008/08/oranginas-beastly-ad-shakes-up-uk.html|archive-date=2011-07-17}}</ref>。2008年4月時，該廣告在線上的觀看次數已達300萬次<ref name="talkingretail"/>。

